# DEPRECATED - kept for reference only.
#
# As of the single-.env consolidation, all SEO keys (Bing Webmaster,
# Google PageSpeed, Google OAuth Desktop JSON path, GA4 property id) live in
# the repo root `.env` file, not in a separate `.env.seo.local` file.
#
# Copy `.env.example` to `.env` and fill in the SEO section there. The
# `scripts/seo/*` scripts read `.env` directly.
#
# If you keep a `.env.seo.local` file for legacy reasons, the SEO scripts
# will still read it (it wins over `.env` for matching keys), but you do not
# need to maintain it.
#
# Setup walkthrough: `docs/SEO_API_SETUP_GUIDE_2026-04-29.md`
